title: X-Ray & Imaging Patient Access
description:
X-Ray & Imaging Patient Access App is used by patients to access their images and reports of examinations performed at X-Ray & Imaging.


When your images are ready to view, you will receive an SMS link to activate your account. Click on the secure link and follow the prompts to activate your account.


Once activated, you will be able to use this account to access all future studies performed at X-Ray & Imaging.


We will provide your referring health professional with the report of your examination shortly after your appointment. The report will be available to you on the Patient App 14 days following your scan and the report button will become active at this time.
